Title: MEHAR READY NEBO PISTON COMPRESSOR Nebulizer(White)
Description: Mehar ready Nebo is designed to deliver the prescribed medication solution to treat patient respiratory disorders such as asthma, allergies and bronchitis. Mehar Ready Nebo Compressor Nebulizer is comprised of four parts, the compressor unit, nebulizer cup, tube and mouthpiece . The device can provide medication to the lower airways of body at an average rate of 0.2 ml per minute. The nebulizer utilizes compressed air that flows at high speed via liquid medicine in the cup, converting into mist or aerosol thereby making it easy for users to inhale the right quantity of effective medicine. Mehar Ready Nebo can be used through mouthpiece, nosepiece and the child mask or adult mask. Further, this equipment needs to be cleaned after every usage. You just have to take all the parts of the nebulizer and wash them (excluding the tubing and finger valve) in water and liquid dish soap. Shake it after the wash to remove excess water and store it dry.

Description: Bio Fresh Yoghurt of Bulgaria Probiotic Day Cream, Collagen Expert with Rose Oil - 50ml:Rose products are from the NATURAL roses of Rose Valley in Bulgaria-Kazanlak, extracted from the "Rosa Damascena " by steam distillation. Production of rose and rose oil in Bulgaria-Kazanlak has started 16th century and today the region is the biggest rose oil exporter. Around 4000 kg of fresh roses distilled to get just 1 kg of high quality rose oil.There are two main Rose Oil types; Rose ottos are extracted through steam distillation, while rose absolutes are obtained through solvent extraction or supercritical carbon dioxide extraction, with the absolute being used more commonly in perfumery. Even with their high price and the advent of organic synthesis, rose oils are still perhaps the most widely used essential oil in perfumery.Bulgaria produces about 70% of all rose oil in the world.A new revolutionary product containing extremely effective active ingredients - a probiotic of Yogurt and natural Bulgarian rose oil. The yoghurt probiotic was synthesized from living bacterial cells of Lactobacillus Bulgaricus and isolated from them using sophicticated technological processes. the priceless probiotic product, combined with natural rose oil, is a powerful cellular regenerator. It simulates intenselythe synthesis of collagen and elastin - a guarantee for intensive smoothing action and prevention of appearance of wrinkles .The content includes also UV filter preventing premature sun damage and the appearance of liver spots .The product protects from external influences and stimulates the restorative processes in the skin. It is renewed, hydrated and more youthful looking. The product is suitable under-makeup primer . Paraben FREEIngredients:•Aqua•Glycerin•Rosa Damascena Flower Oil•Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil•Lactobacillus Bulgaricus Ferment Filtrate•Citronellol•Hydrolyzed Yoghurt Protein•Cera Alba Direction for Use: Apply the cream every morning on cleansed skin with light massaging movements.
